Ask HN: Who wants a LED that blinks every time a new HN article is posted?
text: Silly idea, but I noticed that the articles are not posted very frequently - perhaps every few seconds. For some reason it seems that it would be satisfying/funny to have an old school LED that blinks every time one is posted. Pointless of course.
